metadata.name: Last Sunset of 2020
metadata.description:
Bye bye 2020.
This is the last ray of sunshine I saw in 2020.
A special year for humanity with Covid19 and lockdowns, but a year full of extraordinary things for my family, my friends and me.
A year where the reduction of possibilities allowed me to refocus and decide to go as far as possible in what I love: photography, travel and sport.
